{"name":"Checkbox-and-radiobox-css","tagline":"Style Checkbox and Radiobox.","body":"# Checkbox-And-Radiobox-CSS\r\nStyle Checkbox and Radiobox.\r\n\r\n## Installation\r\nOnly add style CSS.\r\n\r\n**Style CSS**\r\n```html\r\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"checkbox-radiobox.css\">\r\n```\r\n\r\n## HTML\r\n\r\n**Checkbox**\r\n```html\r\n<div class=\"md-checkbox\">\r\n\t<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"idCheckbox1\">\r\n\t<label for=\"idCheckbox1\">\r\n\t\t<span class=\"check\"></span>\r\n\t\t<span class=\"box\"></span>\r\n\t\tOption 1\r\n\t</label>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"md-checkbox\">\r\n\t<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"idCheckbox2\">\r\n\t<label for=\"idCheckbox2\">\r\n\t\t<span class=\"check\"></span>\r\n\t\t<span class=\"box\"></span>\r\n\t\tOption 2\r\n\t</label>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Radiobox**\r\n```html\r\n<div class=\"md-radio\">\r\n\t<input type=\"radio\" id=\"idRadio1\" name=\"radio1\">\r\n\t<label for=\"idRadio1\">\r\n\t\t<span class=\"check\"></span>\r\n\t\t<span class=\"box\"></span>\r\n\t\tOption 1\r\n\t</label>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"md-radio\">\r\n\t<input type=\"radio\" id=\"idRadio2\" name=\"radio1\">\r\n\t<label for=\"idRadio2\">\r\n\t\t<span class=\"check\"></span>\r\n\t\t<span class=\"box\"></span>\r\n\t\tOption 2\r\n\t</label>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n","google":"","note":"Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration."}